30
00:02:02.623 --> 00:02:05.659
MILLIE: Wow. um.
you're just. this is...

31
00:02:06.461 --> 00:02:08.463
I... I...

32
00:02:08.497 --> 00:02:11.832
I'm just going to say.
I think you might be
overqualified for this job

33
00:02:11.866 --> 00:02:14.102
