this entire house soup to nuts.

64
00:03:19.568 --> 00:03:20.701
He's an architect?

65
00:03:20.734 --> 00:03:22.003
No. he's in tech.

66
00:03:22.037 --> 00:03:24.638
But he pays
incredible attention

67
00:03:24.672 --> 00:03:25.974
