68
00:03:26.007 --> 00:03:29.511
Now. these steps are. uh.
kind of nuts. I know.

69
00:03:29.544 --> 00:03:32.280
Andrew says I'm totally gonna
kill myself one day on these.

70
00:03:32.813 --> 00:03:34.316
I'm such a klutz.

71
00:03:34.349 --> 00:03:36.817
I should just draw
my chalk outline on the bottom

72
00:03:36.851 --> 00:03:37.953
and get it over with.

73
00:03:37.986 --> 00:03:39.254
So there's another set
of stairs

74
00:03:39.287 --> 00:03:40.322
on the other side of the house

75
00:03:40.355 --> 00:03:42.090
